lyrics:
[Verse]
I'm laughing so hard right now, can't contain my glee
But the most annoying person is the teacher's pet, you see
Always raising their hand, trying to impress
Oh, they think they're so perfect, it's hard to digest

[Chorus]
Teacher's pet, oh so eager and uptight
Always ready to prove they're oh-so-bright
But we see through their act, they just want to please
Oh, they're the teacher's pet, but they can't fool me
